			(property "Description" "N-channel enhancement-mode MOSFET, 60V/300mA, SOT-23. Used as an open-drain HPD pulldown driven directly from a 3.3V FPGA GPIO (Vgs(th) ~2.1V typ, well within 3.3V logic drive) -- the HDMI source provides the 5V HPD pull-up per spec, so no pull-up is needed on the sink (our) side. Pinout (SOT-23, pin1=G/pin2=S/pin3=D) cross-checked against Nexperia, Microchip, ON Semi and ST datasheets, all in agreement."
				(at 0 0 0)
				(show_name no)
				(do_not_autoplace no)
				(hide yes)
				(effects
					(font
						(size 1.27 1.27)
					)
